quran[15{c,v,t}:
23,90,"jo amar haq hai woh hum inn ke samnay le aeye hain, aur koi shak nahi ke yeh log jhutay hain"
23,91,"Allah ne kisi ko apni aulaad nahi banaya hai aur koi dosra khuda uss ke sath nahi hai agar aisa hota to har khuda apni Khalq ko le kar allag ho jata, aur phir woh aik dosray par charh dorrtay pak hai Allah un baton se jo yeh log banatay hain"
23,92,"khulay aur chupay ka jan-nay wala, woh balatar hai uss shirk se jo yeh log tajweez kar rahay hain"
23,93,"ae Muhammad Sallallahu Alaihi Wasallam, dua karo ke"" parvar-digaar, jis azaab ki inn ko dhamki di ja rahi hai woh agar meri mojoodgi mein to laaye"
23,94,"to ae mere rab, mujhe un zalim logon mein shaamil nah kejio """
23,95,aur haqeeqat yeh hai ke hum tumhari aankhon ke samnay hi woh cheez le anay ki poori qudrat rakhtay hain jis ki dhamki hum inhen day rahay hain
23,96,"ae NabiSallallahu Alaihi Wasallam, buraiee ko is tareeqa se dafaa karo jo behtareen ho jo kuch baatein woh tum par banatay hain woh hamein khoob maloom hain"
23,97,"aur dua karo ke"" parvar-digaar, mein shyatin ki uksahaton seteri panah mangta hon"
23,98,"balkay ae mere rab, mein to is se bhi teri panah mangta hon ke woh mere paas ayen """
23,99,"( yeh log apni karni se baz nah ayen ge ) yahan taq ke jab un mein se kisi ko mout aa jaye gi to kehna shuru kere ga ke"" ae mere rab, mujhe usi duniya mein wapas bhaij degiye jisay mein chore aaya hon"
23,100,"umeed hai ke ab mein naik amal karoon ga"" hargiz nahi, yeh bas aik baat hai jo woh buk raha hai ab inn sab ( marnay walon ) ke peechay aik barzakh haail hai doosri zindagi ke din taq"
23,101,"phir jounhi ke sor phoonk diya gaya, un ke darmain phir koi rishta nah rahay ga aur nah woh aik dosray ko poucheen ge"
23,102,uss waqt jin ke plrhe bhaari hon ge wohi Falah payen ge
23,103,aur jin ke plrhe halkay hon ge wohi log hon ge jinhon ne apne aap ko ghatay mein daal liya woh jahannum mein hamesha rahen ge
23,104,aag un ke cheharon ki khaal chaat jaye gi aur unn ke jabray bahar nikal ayen ge
